{
  "texts": [
    "Rather, the result indicates those who have higher exposure to AI tend to have more positive sentiments.",
    "This was also the case when the analysis is focused on generation AIs for image and language.",
    "RQ3: how do people interact with generative AI?Going beyond how people perceive generative AI, in our RQ3, we aim to get insights into how people \"use\" generative AI through the lens of ChatGPT, which has brought significant global interest in generative AI [5].",
    "In particular, a trend of posting screenshots of their usage of ChatGPT on social media [30] provides an invaluable resource for our investigation.",
    "In contrast to image-generative AI tools that have a very focused usage, ChatGPT can be used for many different scenarios."
  ]
}